						               													<description>Solo card survival game in which we try to survive in the huge forest. While wandering we have to take care of food, water, shelter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We create a map of random cards on which are marked subsequent locations, in each of them we can perform different actions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In his turn, the player chooses a place to go on the map made of cards, then draws an 'action' card that specifies what he can do at that location. Each action can be done by a dice roll action based on the 'push your luck' mechanic or by spending 'fatigue' points (which he will also lose if he fails, but more). When he runs out of 'fatigue' points he has to pay with health points, their end means losing the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In some locations, we will be able to get raw materials (5 types), which will be used for crafting items that will help to significantly increase the chances of testing for certain actions (e.g. bow increases the chances of hunting).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game takes place in different scenarios with specific victory conditions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
